02:54.875 --> 02:57.476
It gets a lot worse than just
a fuckin' alarm system.

03:13.293 --> 03:14.993
This needs to be surgical.

03:14.995 --> 03:17.262
No mistakes. We gotta cover all the angles.

03:17.264 --> 03:19.731
It's gonna take time to plan this.

03:19.733 --> 03:22.968
Six weeks, that's what we've got.

03:22.970 --> 03:24.503
You can't rush this.

03:24.505 --> 03:27.105
We got six weeks or this doesn't happen.

03:27.107 --> 03:28.273
If you can't do it, tell us now

03:28.275 --> 03:30.776
so I can find someone who can.

03:30.778 --> 03:33.712
All I'm saying is that
I've been doin' this

03:33.714 --> 03:36.715
for long enough to know that
there are only two outcomes

03:36.717 --> 03:39.284
to this little situation of ours.

03:39.286 --> 03:43.755
One is where we plan this properly.

03:43.757 --> 03:46.958
The second is where we don't get caught.

03:46.960 --> 03:49.728
Look, none of us are here
because we wanna be.

03:49.730 --> 03:51.463
Okay, this is the last chance
we're gonna get

03:51.465 --> 03:53.532
at a normal fuckin' life.

03:53.534 --> 03:54.766
We've taken things this far

03:54.768 --> 03:56.835
because we all understand
the risks involved.

03:59.005 --> 04:00.906
They're completely predictable.

04:00.908 --> 04:01.907
Yeah, that's the first mistake.

04:01.909 --> 04:04.509
We can't assume anything on this job.

04:04.511 --> 04:07.512
He's got access to diamonds.

04:07.514 --> 04:08.947
A lot of diamonds.

04:08.949 --> 04:11.016
Owns a chain of distributors.

04:11.018 --> 04:12.784
Has access to all the safes all the time.

04:12.786 --> 04:15.053
Expect the unexpected,
that's all I'm saying.

04:15.055 --> 04:18.423
Coming from a guy
that's been in prison twice.

04:18.425 --> 04:20.858
Third time, they throw away the
key. You know that, don't you?

04:20.861 --> 04:23.161
Yeah, we're gonna learn
from your mistakes.

04:23.163 --> 04:25.797
That's why we're cousins.

04:25.799 --> 04:27.399
Yeah, that's a zippy new hairdo

04:27.401 --> 04:29.401
you got there, Goldilocks.

04:29.403 --> 04:31.136
You hiding from someone?

04:31.138 --> 04:33.205
Are you running away from something?

04:35.274 --> 04:38.043
Sometimes, all you can do is run, Mark.

04:38.045 --> 04:40.612
I think we can all agree on one thing.

04:40.614 --> 04:42.681
The sooner we get this
over with, the better.

04:46.586 --> 04:48.787
This thing has to go down
without a glitch.

04:48.789 --> 04:51.423
It needs to tick-tick like a Swiss watch.

05:14.147 --> 05:15.947
You boys all good?

05:15.949 --> 05:19.017
Apart from freezing my balls
off, I'm just peachy.

05:20.653 --> 05:22.721
You have balls, James?

05:25.057 --> 05:26.458
Turn right here.

05:53.653 --> 05:56.221
Hey, protection only.

05:56.223 --> 05:58.523
Yeah, for protection only.

06:02.495 --> 06:05.363
Ade, take the front.
James, take the back.

06:05.365 --> 06:06.798
Yeah, got it.

06:08.201 --> 06:10.268
- Okay, you ready?
- Yup.

06:12.905 --> 06:15.173
