Don't believe them!

15:15.248 --> 15:17.181
You know the rules here.

15:17.183 --> 15:20.885
The quicker we get this done,
the quicker you go home.

15:25.257 --> 15:26.724
Take two.

15:28.327 --> 15:30.795
Mr. and Mrs. Hudson,
we have your daughter...

15:30.797 --> 15:33.064
don't pay them, daddy!
They're in over their heads.

15:33.066 --> 15:35.733
Hey, hey, stop. I got this.

15:35.735 --> 15:37.268
