15:40.739 --> 15:42.573
Hey.

15:42.575 --> 15:44.642
You wanna know a secret?

15:46.612 --> 15:48.980
You're gonna make it out of this unharmed.

15:48.982 --> 15:51.049
Okay? This..

15:52.017 --> 15:53.818
It's all for show.

15:53.820 --> 15:55.953
The last thing we wanna do is hurt you.

15:57.489 --> 16:00.792
Now I know you love your dad very much.

16:00.794 --> 16:02.460
He's done bad things to some people.

16:02.462 --> 16:04.595
Taken things that don't belong to him.

16:07.766 --> 16:09.333
Now your daddy's rich.

16:10.769 --> 16:14.105
What we're taking,
he'll make up very quickly.

16:14.107 --> 16:17.175
This is just what we have to do
to get the money.

16:17.177 --> 16:20.878
It'll all be over
very, very quick if you behave.

16:23.949 --> 16:27.051
Rehearsal's over, okay?

16:29.054 --> 16:30.521
Okay?

16:31.723 --> 16:33.191
Okay.

16:36.261 --> 16:40.264
Mr. and Mrs. Hudson,
here is your daughter.

16:40.266 --> 16:42.800
She's having a really bad night.

16:42.802 --> 16:45.002
We want the 300 carats of diamonds

16:45.004 --> 16:47.638
you keep in your various premises.

16:47.640 --> 16:49.841
This is a time-sensitive matter for us.

16:51.276 --> 16:53.478
Mom, dad, please do what they say.

16:53.480 --> 16:56.314
Give them the diamonds, please!
I wanna come home!

16:56.316 --> 16:58.583
I wanna come home, please!

17:00.385 --> 17:02.520
Send it. I'll make the call.

17:16.435 --> 17:18.136
No one's answering!

17:18.137 --> 17:19.537
Try again.

17:34.853 --> 17:37.155
- The number you have reached is not in service.
- Shit.

17:38.357 --> 17:40.424
Try their cell phones.

17:56.108 --> 17:57.642
