these are the right numbers?

17:57.644 --> 17:59.610
Yeah, I checked them over and over.

18:00.880 --> 18:02.046
Fuck!

18:02.048 --> 18:04.448
You wanna wait it out?

18:04.450 --> 18:05.883
Because you're the one who said

18:05.885 --> 18:07.852
this thing needed to be slick, quiet

18:07.854 --> 18:09.554
and most importantly, fast!

18:09.556 --> 18:10.888
I know what I fucking said!

18:10.890 --> 18:12.423
Haze, you need to stay calm.

18:12.425 --> 18:14.492
This is me calm.

18:34.613 --> 18:35.713
You guys need to go back to the house.

18:35.715 --> 18:39.250
- No.
- No? That's it?

18:39.252 --> 18:41.419
You wanna bring somethin' else
to the table here?

18:41.421 --> 18:43.020
That's not the plan.

18:43.022 --> 18:44.789
Yeah, it is the plan.

18:44.791 --> 18:46.857
It's called plan B.

18:50.329 --> 18:51.562
What if it's a trap?

18:51.564 --> 18:54.232
They don't know
what they're tryin' to trap.

18:54.234 --> 18:56.601
We haven't made contact yet!

18:56.603 --> 18:58.736
There's no way they've watched the video

18:58.738 --> 19:01.339
and gone to the cops
in the last three minutes.

19:01.341 --> 19:04.075
We can't babysit this girl
for days, alright?

19:04.077 --> 19:05.610
People are gonna know
that I'm up to something.

19:05.612 --> 19:07.144
I've got a court date in three days

19:07.146 --> 19:08.679
and I need to be out
of the fucking country.

19:08.681 --> 19:09.880
I need to be in Panama.

19:09.882 --> 19:12.016
This deal needs to go down like we planned.

19:12.018 --> 19:14.085
