19:22.527 --> 19:24.595
I'm with you, cuz.

19:29.234 --> 19:31.836
Just scope it out. Stay in touch.

19:37.175 --> 19:40.611
You hear anything, you let us know.

19:40.613 --> 19:42.313
Yeah, I gotcha.

19:44.082 --> 19:45.316
Hey.

19:47.452 --> 19:50.388
You be careful, okay?

19:51.723 --> 19:53.224
Yeah.

20:19.785 --> 20:23.020
The wiring in this place is fucked up.

20:24.923 --> 20:27.158
Just go. No one's afraid of the dark.

20:29.761 --> 20:31.829
