21:37.463 --> 21:39.530
Yeah, man, this is a fuck-up!

21:44.936 --> 21:47.371
Keep your eyes on the road.

21:48.907 --> 21:52.443
Let's at least try not to kill
another family member.

21:54.379 --> 21:55.946
Nice.

22:49.935 --> 22:52.470
That's a good girl.

22:52.472 --> 22:54.538
You just stay there.

23:58.637 --> 24:00.704
You should really let me go.

24:01.907 --> 24:04.041
