39:03.642 --> 39:05.208
Come on.

40:14.645 --> 40:16.246
Mark?

40:18.282 --> 40:19.883
Mark?

40:23.754 --> 40:25.255
Mark?

40:37.601 --> 40:38.968
Mark?

41:00.224 --> 41:01.658
