43:28.739 --> 43:30.440
James!

43:30.442 --> 43:31.441
Dude, what the fuck are you doing?

43:31.443 --> 43:33.276
Come on, we gotta get back. Hey.

43:34.778 --> 43:37.947
Ade, I saw my mom.

43:37.949 --> 43:39.549
