43:39.551 --> 43:42.385
She came back to fuck me up even more.

43:42.387 --> 43:43.853
Hey, listen to me.

43:43.855 --> 43:46.022
Alright, your mom died
five fuckin' years ago.

43:46.024 --> 43:48.091
Okay, that bitch is in hell. Now come on!

44:00.571 --> 44:02.071
Fuck!

44:03.540 --> 44:05.174
Hazel!

44:09.113 --> 44:10.947
What happened?

44:35.806 --> 44:37.673
